'''Katsura Shrine''' (かつらじんじゃ) is a {{ill|lt=Shinto shrine|Q845945|qid=Q845945|1=Shinto shrine}} in {{ill|lt=Katsura-chō|Q11400186|qid=Q11400186|1=Katsura chō}}, {{ill|lt=Tokushima|Q207309|qid=Q207309|1=Tokushima (city)}}, {{ill|lt=Tokushima Prefecture|Q160734|qid=Q160734|1=Tokushima Prefecture}}.

=== History ===
Its founding period is unknown<ref name=":0">''{{ill|lt=Kadokawa Nihon Chimei Daijiten|Q4093011|qid=Q4093011|1=Kadokawa Nihon Chimei Daijiten}} 36 Tokushima Prefecture'' ({{ill|lt=1986|Q2430|qid=Q2430|1=1986}} ISBN 4040013603)</ref>. Up to {{ill|lt=1875|Q7764|qid=Q7764|1=1875}} (Meiji 8), it was called Sugiō Daimyōjin, and there is a theory that {{ill|lt=Susanoo|Q272993|qid=Q272993|lt=Susanoo-no-Mikoto|1=Susanoo-no-Mikoto}} was its deity<ref name=":0" />.

It is said that on the lunar date of March 10 in {{ill|lt=1184|Q19728|qid=Q19728|1=1184}} (Genryaku 1), {{ill|lt=Minamoto no Yoshitsune|Q310445|qid=Q310445|1=Minamoto no Yoshitsune}} worshipped here while heading for {{ill|lt=Yashima|Q11465681|qid=Q11465681|1=Yashima}}<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{ill|lt=2000|Q1985|qid=Q1985|1=2000}}, {{ill|lt=Heibonsha|Q11482108|qid=Q11482108|1=Heibonsha}}, ''Place Names of Tokushima Prefecture''</ref>.

=== Enshrined deities ===
* {{ill|lt=Ōkuninushi|Q276944|qid=Q276944|lt=Ōnamuchi-no-Mikoto|1=Ōkuninushi}}
* Associated deities - {{ill|qid=Q8009611|lt=Kotoshironushi|Q8009611|qid=Q8009611|qid=Q8009611|lt=Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto|1=Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto}}, {{ill|lt=Suseribime|Q8191715|qid=Q8191715|lt=Suserihime-no-Mikoto|1=Suseri-Hime}}, {{ill|lt=Sukunabikona|Q3275687|qid=Q3275687|lt=Sukunabikona-no-Mikoto|1=Sukunabikona}}, {{ill|lt=Tamakushihime|Q11572681|qid=Q11572681|lt=Tamakushihime-no-Mikoto|1=Tamakushi-hime}}, {{ill|qid=Q386563|lt=Ōyamatsumi|Q386563|qid=Q386563|qid=Q386563|lt=Ōyamatsumi-no-Mikoto|1=Ōyamatsumi}}

=== Sessha and Massha ===
* Konpira-gū, Fukeburi-gū, Akiba Shrine, Jisha Shrine

=== Festivals ===
* Summer grand festival - {{ill|lt=July 9|Q2690|qid=Q2690|1=July 9}}
* Autumn grand festival - {{ill|lt=October 9|Q2923|qid=Q2923|1=October 9}}

=== Access ===
* About 15 minutes on foot from {{ill|lt=Jizōbashi Station|Q6203576|qid=Q6203576|1=Jizōbashi Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Mugi Line|Q860478|qid=Q860478|1=Mugi Line}} of {{ill|lt=JR Shikoku|Q496531|qid=Q496531|lt=JR|1=Shikoku Railway Company}}.
* About 20 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Tokushima Interchange|Q11071632|qid=Q11071632|1=Tokushima interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Tokushima Expressway|Q11490216|qid=Q11490216|1=Tokushima Expressway}}.

